("SHOULD", "SHOULD NOT", "RECOMMENDED", "MAY", and "OPTIONAL" in Library) show newline
(of Cyberspace documents are to be interpreted as described in RFC 2119) show newline
(and RFC 8174.[^r1]) show newline
() show newline
([^r1]: Research: RFC 2119 keywords provide precise normative language.) show newline
(Implementations can be validated against MUST requirements. SHOULD) show newline
(indicates strong recommendation with documented exceptions.) show newline
